# Building

### Build for Android
Use `qmake`:

```bash
# Clone the code
git clone https://invent.kde.org/kde/vvave.git
cd vvave
# Create build dir
mkdir build && cd build
# Build
qmake -o Makefile ../vvave.pro
make
```

